### 4. Update Review [AUTHENTICATED]
# Requires: valid review ID, at least one field to update
# Can update: rating (1-5), comment
# Response: 200 OK with updated review object
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reviews/{{reviewId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

